            . I <rs id="t17700912-87-viclabel410" type="occupation">keep the <placeName id="t17700912-87-crimeloc411">Cock, at the side of the Fleet-market</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t17700912-87-crimeloc411" type="placeName" value="Cock, at the side of the Fleet-market"></interp>
